{"tid":629725,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭中基若封帝感謝太太","createTime":"2018-04-15T03:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T03:14:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d36ed2602d55d5ebb5e9927c5c9314459d530822","tid":629725,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:06:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180415/20361762?_ga=2.49456806.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F20361762%3F_ga%3D2.49456806.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=e2PC5uQKZy0AmFTAHjyWpjANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=fbb3f1cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F20361762%3F_ga%3D2.49456806.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=2a2ca605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180415/20361762?_ga=2.49456806.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭中基若封帝感謝太太<br />\n<br />\n2.6K<br />\n娛樂名人<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180415/large/15ec6p11e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180415%2Flarge%2F15ec6p11e.jpg&h=85de0538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭中基對於奪獎的信心，笑說永遠覺得對手做得比自己好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄭中基在《低俗喜劇》的「暴龍哥」角色深入民心，當年為他贏得金像獎最佳男配角，今再憑《大樂師．為愛配樂》首度挑戰影帝。鄭中基笑言上次領獎時沒想過感言：「上次冇諗所以講咁耐。同埋漏咗好多人，導演彭浩翔都冇多謝，仲有阿澤，唔止冇多謝我個女。如果今次會多謝太太，同一定記得多謝導演，仲有田啟文，係佢叫我試下，冇做過呢類戲。」<br />\n<br />\n對於今次奪獎信心，鄭中基說：「往往都係咁，自己睇自己，同自己睇人哋，你永遠覺得人哋做得好啲。你睇佢呢場戲做得幾好，一場已經頂我幾場，就算當年攞男配，人人覺得我係熱門。」他反而最想金培達贏及毛舜筠攞獎：「上次同毛姐合作《老港正傳》，覺得毛姐已應該攞。」<br />\n採訪：何永寧<br />\n攝影：陳慧安<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180415/large/15ec6p12e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180415%2Flarge%2F15ec6p12e.jpg&h=bc5339fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭中基憑《大樂師．為愛配樂》首度入圍最佳男主角。劇照<br />\n<br />\n【最佳男主角提名】<br />\n<br />\n鄭中基《大樂師．為愛配樂》<br />\n劉德華《拆彈專家》<br />\n田壯壯《相愛相親》<br />\n古天樂《殺破狼．貪狼》<br />\n凌文龍《黃金花》<br />\n資料來源：金像獎大會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180415/large/15ec6p16e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180415%2Flarge%2F15ec6p16e.jpg&h=e1bf68f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古天樂《殺破狼．貪狼》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n娜姐攞獎死而無憾<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n毛舜筠了解對手<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n凌文龍佛系爭獎<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n被毛舜筠演技震撼視為勁敵Stephy爭影后：未識得緊張<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚 2000-2330 第37屆香港電影金像獎頒獎典禮 ViuTV 99台 (4月15日 星期日)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/629720/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/629720/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fdce08398f48badcb6b35179b7dba22c9b966d33","tid":629725,"uid":89061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:09:38.000Z","msg":"今年啲提名好似咁弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暴龍哥好大機會"},{"pid":"e03c5a3e786ba7297493b7b1ae1c7bcc541d6bc7","tid":629725,"uid":124450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:12:36.000Z","msg":"第38屆香港金像獎最佳男主角goes to...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《拆彈專家》，劉、德、華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8949ad435f255a92761b3433a491978f77e4e3f7","tid":629725,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:1